nodes.text: Jokskk Quosto was a male Selkath who lived on Coruscant during the Cold War with the resurgent Sith Empire.

A Selkath male, Jokskk Ouosto lived on the planet Coruscant where he worked at the Senate Commercial District below the Senate Building during the Cold War between the Galactic Republic and the resurgent Sith Empire. A bioanalyst, Quosto made a living passing on his knowledge of his trade to those who wished to learn.
Jokskk Quosto appears in the BioWare MMORPG Star Wars: The Old Republic as a skill trainer for Bioanalysis on Coruscant.
